        "comment": "Refer to {{v2-table:0385:Manufacturer identifier}} in Chapter 2C, Code Tables, for suggested values, or relevant external code sets may be used (e.g., HIBCC Manufacturers Labeler ID Code (LIC), UPC, NDC).",
